  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive at any cost is the only goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do this, you will have to overcome difficulties such as cold, thirst and hunger. Make a fire, build a shelter, kill animals and explore abandoned cities. Protect yourself from infected and other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do whatever it takes to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788040/extras/7f504e4b14f0a9c4939ee9e2069b2ed5.avif?t=1745619523\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open World Zombie Survival Game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through a devastated post apocalyptic world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight zombies, human survivors and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control of various types of cars and other unusual equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find many different firearms, melee weapons, clothing and different types of equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade with survivors in shelters or safe zones to get the necessary equipment.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788040/extras/71e85139cce54f64733dcf4fd37fab39.avif?t=1745619523\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planned features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer survival with player run servers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story system linking into the quests. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vehicle customisation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788040/extras/b51c00a6de47712c0b8fbe31a52ed926.avif?t=1745619523\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive at any cost is the only goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do this, you will have to overcome difficulties such as cold, thirst and hunger. Make a fire, build a shelter, kill animals and explore abandoned cities. Protect yourself from infected and other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do whatever it takes to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788040/extras/7f504e4b14f0a9c4939ee9e2069b2ed5.avif?t=1745619523\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open World Zombie Survival Game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through a devastated post apocalyptic world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight zombies, human survivors and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control of various types of cars and other unusual equipment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find many different firearms, melee weapons, clothing and different types of equipment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade with survivors in shelters or safe zones to get the necessary equipment.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2788040/extras/71e85139cce54f64733dcf4fd37fab39.avif?t=1745619523\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planned features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer survival with player run servers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story system linking into the quests. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\